ng=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">Change Date</span></span></h3> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">January 28, 2016</span></span></div> </td> </tr> </tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">II.iii.2.C.2.a<a id=\"2a\" name=\"2a\">.</a>  Responsibilities of the Rating Activity</span></span></h3> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">The rating activity is responsible for evaluating disabilities under the applicable laws and rating schedule, including statutory benefits such as</span></span></div> <ul> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">loss or loss of use of various body organs or parts</span></span></div> </li> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">SMP, other than aid and attendance (A&amp;A) awarded to patients in nursing homes, and</span></span></div> </li> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">SMC.</span></span></div> </li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"height: 89px; width: 654px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">II.iii.2.C.2.b<a id=\"2b\" name=\"2b\">.</a>  Claims for Increase in the Level of Disability</span></span></h3> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">Refer any claim for increase in the level of disability to the rating activity for action after completing any necessary development actions. </span></span></div> <div></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><strong><em>Reference</em></strong>:  For information on requesting records and when to order an examination, see <a articleid=\"554400000014102\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part III, Subpart i, Chapter 2, Section C - Duty to Assist With Obtaining Records\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000014102/M21-1-Part-III-Subpart-i-Chapter-2-Section-C-Duty-to-Assist-With-Obtaining-Records\">M21-1, Part III, Subpart i, 2.C</a>. </span></span></div> </td> </tr> </tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"></div><div class=\"ng-scope\"><br/> </div><h2 class=\"ng-scope\"><br/><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">3<a id=\"3\" name=\"3\">.</a>  Interpreting Submissions for Increased Compensation</span></strong></span></span></h2><div class=\"ng-scope\"><br/> </div><div class=\"ng-scope\"></div><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><div class=\"ng-scope\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <div> <h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">Introduction</span></span></h3> </div> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"> <div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">This topic contains procedures for interpreting submissions for increased compensation, including</span></span></div> <ul> <li> <div><a href=\"#3a\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">distinguishing claims for increase from requests for decision review</span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">, and</span></span></div> </li> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><a href=\"#3b\" target=\"_self\">screening submissions for increased compensation</a>.</span></span></div> </li> </ul> </div> </td> </tr> </tbody></table></div><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><div class=\"ng-scope\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <h3><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">Change Date</span></span></strong></h3> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">July 8, 2019</span></span></div> </td> </tr> </tbody></table></div><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">II.iii.2.C.3.a<a id=\"3a\" name=\"3a\">.</a>  Distinguishing Claims for Increase From Requests for Decision Review</span></span></h3> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"> <div> <div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">Under <a href=\"https://www.ecfr.gov/cgi-bin/text-idx?SID=3967d2b525436657ad0fad655ff65e9c&amp;mc=true&amp;node=se38.1.3_12500&amp;rgn=div8\" target=\"_blank\">38 CFR 3.2500(a)(2)</a>, claimants can request a review of a decision issued on a claim at any time after VA issues notice of a decision.  Therefore, screen all submissions regarding evaluation issues to determine the intent of the claimant.  The form used by the claimant will determine whether the submission should be handled as a</span></span></div> <ul> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">claim for increase, or</span></span></div> </li> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">decision review request under <a href=\"https://www.ecfr.gov/cgi-bin/text-idx?SID=3967d2b525436657ad0fad655ff65e9c&amp;mc=true&amp;node=se38.1.3_12500&amp;rgn=div8\" target=\"_blank\">38 CFR 3.2500</a>.</span></span></div> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </td> </tr> </tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><div class=\"ng-scope\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"> <h3><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\">II.iii.2.C.3.b<a id=\"3b\" name=\"3b\">.</a>  Screening Submissions for Increased Compensation</span></span></h3> </td> <td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td> <td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">Screen all submissions for increased compensation based on the table below.</span></span></div> <div></div> <div> <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 508px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\" summary=\"This is an if-then table.  Column 1 contains the criteria and column 2 contains information on how to handle the submission.\" width=\"508\"> <thead> <tr> <th scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 202px; padding: 0px;\"> <div style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><strong>If the claimant submits ...</strong></span></span></div> </th> <th scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 306px; padding: 0px;\"> <div style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><strong>Then handle the submission as a ...</strong></span></span></div> </th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"width: 202px; padding: 0px;\"> <ul> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.vba.va.gov/pubs/forms/VBA-21-526EZ-ARE.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><em>VA Form 21-526EZ</em></a>, or</span></span></div> </li> <li> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">other prescribed form for the increased benefit sought</span></span></div> </li> </ul> </td> <td style=\"width: 306px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">claim for increase.</span></span></div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"width: 202px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.vba.va.gov/pubs/forms/VBA-20-0995-ARE.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><em>VA Form 20-0995, Decision Review Request: Supplemental Claim</em></a></span></span></div> </td> <td style=\"width: 306px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">supplemental claim.</span></span></div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"width: 202px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">evidence regarding an evaluation issue without a prescribed claim form</span></span></div> </td> <td style=\"width: 306px; padding: 0px;\"> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">request for application per <a articleid=\"554400000174879\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, Chapter 2, Section G - Requests for Application and Claims Solicitation\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000174879/M21-1-Part-II-Subpart-iii-Chapter-2-Section-G-Requests-for-Application-and-Claims-Solicitation\">M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, 2.G</a>.</span></span></div> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><strong><em>References</em></strong>:  For more information on </span></span></div> <ul> <li><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">prescribed forms, see <a articleid=\"554400000174869\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, Chapter 1, Section A - Applications for Benefits\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000174869/M21-1-Part-II-Subpart-iii-Chapter-1-Section-A-Applications-for-Benefits\">M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, 1.A</a></span></span></li> <li><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">supplemental claims, see <a articleid=\"554400000174874\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, Chapter 2, Section B - Supplemental Claims\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000174874/M21-1-Part-II-Subpart-iii-Chapter-2-Section-B-Supplemental-Claims\">M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, 2.B</a>, and</span></span></li> <li><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">effective dates for </span></span> <ul> <li><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">claims for increase, see <a articleid=\"554400000180492\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part V, Subpart ii, Chapter 4, Section A - Effective Dates\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000180492/M21-1-Part-V-Subpart-ii-Chapter-4-Section-A-Effective-Dates\">M21-1, Part V, Subpart ii, 4.A.5</a>, and </span></span></li> <li><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif\">supplemental claims, see <a articleid=\"554400000177963\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part X, Subpart ii, Chapter 2, Section A - Revision Based on Specific Types of Submissions, Including Supplemental Claims\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000177963/M21-1-Part-X-Subpart-ii-Chapter-2-Section-A-Revision-Based-on-Specific-Types-of-Submissions-Including-Supplemental-Claims\">M21-1, Part X, Subpart ii, 2.A.3</a>.</span></span></li> </ul> </li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody></table></div><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"> <a articleid=\"554400000174874\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, Chapter 2, Section B - Supplemental Claims\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000174874/M21-1-Part-II-Subpart-iii-Chapter-2-Section-B-Supplemental-Claims\">&lt;--Previous Section</a>  <a articleid=\"554400000174876\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part II, Subpart iii, Chapter 2, Section D - Claims Based on Reports of Examination or Hospitalization\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000174876/M21-1-Part-II-Subpart-iii-Chapter-2-Section-D-Claims-Based-on-Reports-of-Examination-or-Hospitalization\">Next Section--&gt;</a></span></span></div><p class=\"ng-scope\">                <span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><a href=\"#top\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px\">To Top</span></a></span></p><p class=\"ng-scope\"></p></div>\n</div>",
